### Create Collectivity
POST http://localhost:8080/collectivities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "Antananarivo",
  "specialization": "Rice Farming",
  "members": ["{{memberId1}}", "{{memberId2}}"],
  "structure": {
    "president": "{{memberId1}}",
    "vicePresident": "{{memberId2}}",
    "treasurer": "{{memberId3}}",
    "secretary": "{{memberId4}}"
  },
  "federationApproval": true
}

### Get Collectivity
GET http://localhost:8080/collectivities/{{collectivityId}}

### Get All Collectivities
GET http://localhost:8080/collectivities

### Assign Identity to Collectivity
PUT http://localhost:8080/collectivities/{{collectivityId}}/informations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": 101,
  "name": "Collectif Rizteurs Avaradrano"
}

### Get Collectivity Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/collectivities/{{collectivityId}}/transactions?from=2025-01-01&to=2026-12-31

### Create Membership Fees
POST http://localhost:8080/collectivities/{{collectivityId}}/membershipFees
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "eligibleFrom": "2026-01-01",
    "frequency": "MONTHLY",
    "amount": 5000,
    "label": "Cotisation mensuelle"
  },
  {
    "eligibleFrom": "2026-01-01",
    "frequency": "ANNUAL",
    "amount": 50000,
    "label": "Cotisation annuelle obligatoire"
  }
]

### Get Membership Fees
GET http://localhost:8080/collectivities/{{collectivityId}}/membershipFees

### Create Member
POST http://localhost:8080/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "information": {
    "firstName": "Jean",
    "lastName": "Rakoto",
    "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
    "gender": "MALE",
    "address": "Antananarivo",
    "profession": "Farmer",
    "phoneNumber": "0341234567",
    "email": "jean.rakoto{{$randomInt}}@mail.com",
    "occupation": "JUNIOR"
  },
  "collectivityIdentifier": "{{collectivityId}}",
  "referees": [
    {
      "memberIdentifier": "{{memberId1}}",
      "relationshipNature": "friend"
    },
    {
      "memberIdentifier": "{{memberId2}}",
      "relationshipNature": "colleague"
    }
  ],
  "registrationFeePaid": true,
  "membershipDuesPaid": true
}

### Get Member
GET http://localhost:8080/members/{{memberId}}

### Create Member Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/members/{{memberId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "amount": 5000,
    "membershipFeeIdentifier": "{{feeId}}",
    "accountCreditedIdentifier": "{{accountId}}",
    "paymentMode": "CASH"
  }
]

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/ping